data.description:
Gorgeous, remodeled and ready for you! Welcome to the master planned community of Dobson Ranch.
This home is a masterpiece of modern design with a neutral color palette, mixed metals and accent details create a tranquil paradise surpassing expectation. The dual master suite makes this home even more desirable. Upon entering you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that showcases travertine floors throughout (2021-$27,000), 5-inch baseboards, exquisite lighting selections, oversize windows provide a plethora of natural light, cozy brick fireplace and vaulted ceilings that seamlessly flow to beautiful French doors with views to the backyard oasis with a sparkling pool, covered patio and grass area no neighbors behind.  The chef's dream kitchen is an entertainer's delight with expansive quartz counters, an abundance of black cabinetry highlighted by gold tone pulls, breakfast bar island w/seating for 5, roll-out drawers and stainless-steel appliances (2021-$22,500). The elegant dining area opens to the living, great room and kitchen enhances the social dining and culinary experience. 
The owner's ensuite is huge - with a sitting area overlooking the pool private. Ideal for work from home. Dual vanities, new lighting, mirrors, faucets, hardware, and on trend painted cabinets (2021-$2,000) and a walk-in custom closet installed (2021-$4500).
Originally, a four bedroom, the front two bedrooms were converted to a secondary owner's suite with private bath access. The guest bath remodel features include contemporary quartz vanity w/square sink, mirrors, and lighting (2021-$3000). The third bedroom is spacious and peaceful.
Other features include new Tesla charger, Nest Smart thermostats, Samsung front loading washer/dryer included, new garage door opener, accordion blinds, high efficiency windows in the master (2022-$3750).
The community tennis courts are a short walk down the block from the home. The highly sought after Dobson Ranch offers amazing amenities: 7 lakes, golf course, 3 rec centers, community pools, spas, tennis & pickleball courts, with shopping and dining nearby. All for a low HOA.  Fantastic location close to 101, 202, 60 and 10 freeways and a short drive to the airport, malls, and entertainment!
